						<summary>

						<p>This is assignable to <hi rend="bold">Parāntaka I.</hi> It records a gift of 25 sheep for burning a lamp with an <hi rend="italic">uḻakku</hi> of ghee every day in the temple of Mahādēva at Tirukkuṟṟālam by one <hi rend="bold">Nakkan Appi Tirumūrtti.</hi> This is in <hi rend="italic">Vaṭṭeḻuttu</hi> script.</p>						

